element_texts.text:
Dear Andy,
If you can't read this get [Bak?] to help you.
Your letter pleased me mightily and I would have written you long ago but I have been busy writing literature. Your loss will be the gain of future generations, old darling.
I am in [Nagle?] now, having drifted here and there and am leaving Sunday for Richmond where I will put up at the [unclear] and Club.
Here Homer and [unclear] and the rest won't let me alone a minute.
[unclear]
"Come on over Sherry."
"You go ti [unclear]? I got much ti do."
Well, you know how it is. I don't dislike
